Interface DeletePromptDialogFragment.DeleteSectionDialogListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdventureEditView, LibraryEditView
    Enclosing class:
    DeletePromptDialogFragment

    public static interface DeletePromptDialogFragment.DeleteSectionDialogListener
    The activity that creates an instance of this dialog fragment must implement this interface in order to receive event callbacks. Each method passes the DialogFragment in case the host needs to query it.
    Author:
    Braeden Soetaert
